      "rationale": "Three-level Richardson extrapolation was completed at the nominal operating point (3.5 L/min, 2500 RPM). GCI for NIH was 9.4%, which exceeds the 5% target. Monte Carlo sweep used the intermediate grid to manage computational cost. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
